  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Scrap Collector</u> is a game where you stack cards to craft new items, make new buildings, and fight the enemies. An example is if you have a \"Bot\" and place it on to a \"Scrap Pile\", it will spawn material cards that you can use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/f91506f40b885c5655ca91f54022d965.poster.avif?t=1741820676\" width=608 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/f91506f40b885c5655ca91f54022d965.webm?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/f91506f40b885c5655ca91f54022d965.mp4?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Explore</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > \"Explore\" cards allow you to search an area for resources, enemies, or even random encounters! Be careful as somethings are better left unfound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/42485583954abeef5d44750714e3119f.poster.avif?t=1741820676\" width=608 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/42485583954abeef5d44750714e3119f.webm?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/42485583954abeef5d44750714e3119f.mp4?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Combat</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Placing the player or a bot card on an enemy will engage in automatic combat. Fight bugs, hostile people and many other things. You can improve your odds of winning combat by teaming bots up against enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/92732a3943434d69f0813ef62300f789.poster.avif?t=1741820676\" width=608 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/92732a3943434d69f0813ef62300f789.webm?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/92732a3943434d69f0813ef62300f789.mp4?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Researching and Leveling</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You unlock new blueprints by leveling up. Every action the player performs adds exp.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Scrap Collector</u> is a game where you stack cards to craft new items, make new buildings, and fight the enemies. An example is if you have a \"Bot\" and place it on to a \"Scrap Pile\", it will spawn material cards that you can use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/f91506f40b885c5655ca91f54022d965.poster.avif?t=1741820676\" width=608 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/f91506f40b885c5655ca91f54022d965.webm?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/f91506f40b885c5655ca91f54022d965.mp4?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Explore</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > \"Explore\" cards allow you to search an area for resources, enemies, or even random encounters! Be careful as somethings are better left unfound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/42485583954abeef5d44750714e3119f.poster.avif?t=1741820676\" width=608 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/42485583954abeef5d44750714e3119f.webm?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/42485583954abeef5d44750714e3119f.mp4?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Combat</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Placing the player or a bot card on an enemy will engage in automatic combat. Fight bugs, hostile people and many other things. You can improve your odds of winning combat by teaming bots up against enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/92732a3943434d69f0813ef62300f789.poster.avif?t=1741820676\" width=608 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/92732a3943434d69f0813ef62300f789.webm?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/92732a3943434d69f0813ef62300f789.mp4?t=1741820676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Researching and Leveling</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You unlock new blueprints by leveling up. Every action the player performs adds exp.</p>",
